OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be another dry day with
OL,6,Flong periods of sunshine, perhaps
OL,7,Fturning hazy at times with areas of
OL,8,Fhigh cloud. Becoming rather warm
OL,9,Finland by the afternoon but cooler
OL,10,Fnear the east coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will stay dry through the
OL,13,Fevening and overnight. Evening
OL,14,Fsunshine leading to clear spells
OL,15,Fovernight allowing some patchy mist or
OL,16,Ffrost to develop.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
