OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FDry and bright in the
OL,6,Fmorning after a chilly start. Becoming
OL,7,Fwarm again by day, with sunshine
OL,8,Fturning hazy as it becomes cloudier at
OL,9,Ftimes later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHigh
OL,12,Fpressure will maintain mainly dry and
OL,13,Fsettled weather with sunshine at
OL,14,Ftimes, but chance of the odd shower on
OL,15,FSunday and Monday. Quite warm inland
OL,16,Fbut cooler along coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
